{"tid":773966,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【昔日大事】十年前的今天，蕭永方陳兆龍脫下氧氣罩救人殉職...","createTime":"2018-08-10T03:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T09:46:59.000Z","uid":28366,"like":68,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"667b3c24c941124739a66cdab4a33f691703dce4","tid":773966,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/111449_1bd25cdcca3c7efcbc85d79b5854012a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F111449_1bd25cdcca3c7efcbc85d79b5854012a.jpg&h=239df1a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十年前的8月10日，旺角彌敦道嘉禾大廈發生五級大火，事件造成4死55傷，其中兩名死者是消防員，他們分別是消防隊目蕭永方及消防員陳兆龍。<br />\n<br />\n事發時，由於接獲大廈12樓不同單位的居民求救，蕭永方與陳兆龍奉命趕往該層進行搜救。兩人數度冒著自己的生命危險，拯救別人；期間吸入毒煙，也大量消耗呼吸器中的壓縮空氣。<br />\n<br />\n當完成在12樓的任務後，儘管呼吸器內的空氣供應已經有限，但他們繼續進行拯救工作，期間更脫下自己的氧氣罩給受困市民；他們其後在大廈頂層遇到兩名居民，並留在兩名居民身旁給予協助，直至因吸入大量濃煙而不支倒地。<br />\n<br />\n該兩名居民其後獲救，但蕭永方及陳兆龍在送抵醫院時，已證實死亡。他們獲追授金英勇勳章，以表揚他們奮不顧身、捨身救人的高尚情操。"},{"pid":"bff0a7441aedd47bdf504980e25a6a694e17a812","tid":773966,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":48,"score":-47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/22/221743_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F22%2F221743_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d124109e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/22/215945_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F22%2F215945_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=44233259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/22/215950_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F0